Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.67,0:15:42.92,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,KELUARGA VISCOUNT BEIG, AJUDAN, KERABAT
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:44.42,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,STATUS RENDAH
